        "subject": "LU-3081 mdd: rename md_op_spec's no_create bit to sp_is_replay",
        "message": "LU-3081 mdd: rename md_op_spec's no_create bit to sp_is_replay\n\nIn struct md_op_spec the value of the no_create bit just reflects\nwhether the request is replay or not and does not fully control\ncreation.  Rename is accordingly to sp_is_replay.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I9cbe05a4377f48981af8894c04d0e141d04ebf22\n"
